Father Józef Witko: I saw Jesus in a white robe
He is a charismatic.
The Holy Masses for liberation and healing celebrated by him attract crowds.
He was a teenager when inexplicable things began to happen in his life.
Today, through a Franciscan, others experience this.
Witko attracts crowds to the Holy Masses for liberation and healing
Once the parents of a 7-month-old baby came to him, who had a hole in the size of 7.5 mm.
It was to be operated.
Father Józef Witko prayed over him.
On the same day, the boy was taken to the hospital for surgery.
The astonished doctors said: "No surgery is needed, the loss is only 1.5 mm."
My parents cried with happiness.
After another prayer of the Franciscan, the hole disappeared completely.
The priest began to experience the extraordinary actions of the Creator as a teenager.
In his dreams, souls in purgatory came to him asking for help.
I was woken up at night and urged to pray for the dead and those who were dying at that moment – he recalls.
He also experienced the presence of an evil spirit.
And he had a vision of what happens to a man who commits mortal sin.
"My body started to change.
I lost my human qualities and started to take on the appearance of an animal," he says.
An invisible force lifted him up, he could not make a voice.
He felt lost.
Then God showed him help.
"Immersed in the waters of the river symbolizing baptism, I was freed and returned to human form...", he says.
He told no one about these strange experiences.
His vocation matured.
He was 16 years old when he joined the Franciscans.
In his sermons, he wanted not only to talk about Jesus.
He wanted people to experience Him alive.
Members of the charismatic community of Renewal in the Holy Spirit
The healing masses celebrated by Father Witko are attended by many people who hope to get rid of the disease.
The priest emphasizes, however, that their main goal is spiritual healing, not bodily healing.
